{"tid":2512021,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"韓韶禧新瀏海頭勁青春 20歲Ryujin撞樣新女神感不知所措","createTime":"2021-05-01T10:57:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-01T11:03:40.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"15cefc208caf52ed2c9d442a602b0c2c59fa4a42","tid":2512021,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T10:57:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/dCjEaf7E3nibzxUFZlbwGA2A9ag=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JNUTYU4P55HPBNSBVMEDVTSYXU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FdCjEaf7E3nibzxUFZlbwGA2A9ag%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJNUTYU4P55HPBNSBVMEDVTSYXU.jpg&h=bf859c63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n韓國新一代女神、憑話題劇《夫妻的世界》彈起的26歲女星韓韶禧（前譯韓素希），近日忙於孖上位男神宋江拍攝《無法抗拒的他》，為了新劇韓韶禧剪了空氣瀏海頭，顯得青春不少。雖然韓韶禧今年出道只是第4年，但近日亦被出道兩年的女團ITZY的20歲成員Ryujin稱為前輩，事關外界不時指Ryujin撞樣韓韶禧，令Ryujin受寵若驚。<br />\n<br />\n尊稱韓韶禧做前輩<br />\n於今日播出的節目中，在ITZY中被稱爲「撒嬌王」的Ryujin因為撞樣韓韶禧而為人認識，同場的前2NE1成員Sandara問到：「喜歡被稱為藍色頭髮的她，還是長得像韓韶禧？」Ryujin選擇了「藍色頭髮的她」，並謙虛地表示：「聽到別人說我長得像韓韶禧前輩，我都不知所措。」<br />\n<br />\n有望孖女神做代言人<br />\n另外，韓韶禧連日來都有在IG上載靚相，當中她又tag了一間珠寶品牌的IG，而該品牌一直邀請女神全智賢做代言人，未知韓韶禧是為品牌拍攝宣傳照，還是有機會與全智賢一起成為代言人呢？<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/tbM6ZRZaiz2Dnc2_OsoZTnBwPLc=/802x1001/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/XX4VNLGQUJC7BL6DM7DACRKKLY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FtbM6ZRZaiz2Dnc2_OsoZTnBwPLc%3D%2F802x1001%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FXX4VNLGQUJC7BL6DM7DACRKKLY.jpg&h=f6722133&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/4xoKFp466_w7Cm7ltj_hkBuJ8FA=/802x1002/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PVFSNBH5GBADVDWQUOIL4IBGC4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F4xoKFp466_w7Cm7ltj_hkBuJ8FA%3D%2F802x1002%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPVFSNBH5GBADVDWQUOIL4IBGC4.jpg&h=d3cef0b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/iMmHndpwMXxys35IMYHbiP25RnM=/802x601/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ZZ6I4X4TMZBNPIZV553MEAYY4M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FiMmHndpwMXxys35IMYHbiP25RnM%3D%2F802x601%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZZ6I4X4TMZBNPIZV553MEAYY4M.jpg&h=01e48e0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/7kYxS0bOFe0JDCspb8g2Ri8bQS0=/802x605/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/BY4ZEAM3VJBGNC663UMJ6EM3PM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F7kYxS0bOFe0JDCspb8g2Ri8bQS0%3D%2F802x605%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FBY4ZEAM3VJBGNC663UMJ6EM3PM.jpg&h=6a0de51d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/LRik5s-16ssm58HeLyRN2qKV3L4=/802x602/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/5WUJAYRQ4RBIPM6PEUKRA3PIEM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FLRik5s-16ssm58HeLyRN2qKV3L4%3D%2F802x602%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F5WUJAYRQ4RBIPM6PEUKRA3PIEM.jpg&h=0a2e439c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/zu86gQNX9umtgCOuPQrBy8iDpck=/802x802/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/DU7WIYEUXNHX7MAWS7E3AHGQQY